reviewText: My 8-year old and 6-year old have been learning about NASA and the history of America's space program. This video is a perfect supplement for our curriculum. We had a little trouble with the DVD (could only get it to play on our computer, not in our DVD player), so I recommend the streaming versionLots and Lots of Roaring Rockets - Soaring Spacecraft

This was ok. Bought for my 3 year old son who is OBSESSED with rockets. He will watch instructional videos on how to build hobby rockets but even this kind of bored him. There is a section with just videos of rockets set to songs about rockets and that's the only part he likes.
